Collection View Source Heat Map Demo
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph>A Heat Map control has a feature used to bind a collection of group data. This sample demonstrates the creation of a view of a data collection, and it also shows binding the collection to a HMC.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph TextAlignment="Center"><Image Source="Images\Collection View Source Heat Map Demo.png" Height="520" Width="750"/></Paragraph>

<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Features
</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">
<ListItem><Paragraph>Supports binding a collection of data items to a heat map control.</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>

<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Interactive Features</Paragraph>


<List Margin="25,0,0,0">

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The property pannel <Bold>"Sales Details"</Bold> will showcase the properties of the heat map items that are hovered over. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>


<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The slider <Bold>"Adjust Colors"</Bold> will change the interior of a heat map item. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>

</List>


